This paper deals with fraud and malware detection in the Google Play app market, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses machine learning algorithms to analyze app data, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of longitudinal app data, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
